import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Menu } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const Nav = () => {
  return (
      <Menu>
        <Menu.Item
          name='editorials'
         
        >
          Editorials
        </Menu.Item>

        <Menu.Item
          name='reviews'
         
        >
          Reviews
        </Menu.Item>

        <Menu.Item
          name='upcomingEvents'
         
        >
          Upcoming Events
        </Menu.Item>
      </Menu>
  )
}

export default Nav
